# FitTrack Pro Blueprint

Reference [MASTER_BLUEPRINT.md](../../MASTER_BLUEPRINT.md) as the single source of truth.

## Stack

- Node.js 20, Fastify 4, Prisma 5, PostgreSQL 16 + PostGIS, Redis 7
- Flutter 3, Riverpod, Dio, Hive, geolocator, flutter_map

## PostGIS Rules

- Geography columns are `Unsupported()` in Prisma — never use ORM for them
- Writes: `$executeRaw` with `ST_GeogFromText()`
- Reads: `$queryRaw` with `ST_AsGeoJSON()::json`

## API Paths (via gateway :8080)

- Auth: `/api/v1/auth/*`, `/api/v1/users/*` → port 5001
- Ingest/feed: `/api/v1/ingest`, `/api/v1/feed`, GET/DELETE `/api/v1/activities/*` → port 5002
- Analytics: `/api/v1/stats/*`, `/api/v1/segments/*`, POST kudos/comments → port 5003

## Security

- bcrypt 12 rounds, Zod validation on all inputs, parameterized raw SQL only
- Ingest returns 202 immediately; worker processes via Redis BLPOP
